            </V>
            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x228C7973<!--I've been friendly with Layne for a long time. Did you know the first band he had was a cottagecore deal? You should have seen the outfits he had. "Galloping Goat Graces" was the first song he put out. --></T>
                  <T>0xCEEDD4F9<!--My mind must be playing tricks on me, given that these things couldn't possibly exist, but after my accident it's almost like I have new...abilities. They felt like some sort of evil manifestation; if such abilities were real, I wonder if they'd all be evil, or if some might be more benign. But how would you even get them? After all, ghosts don't exist!--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
            <V n="title" t="enabled">
              <T n="enabled">0xEBB55930<!--Ravenwood Rumors--></T>
            </V>
            <E n="visual_type">SPEECH</E>
